    type: "section"
    title: "The Shadow’s Reflection"
    excerpt: "The shadow twisted and turned, matching Boof’s steps but sometimes leading the way. It seemed to know the path Boof sought but refused to show the way forward. The boonberries above them dimmed, casting the world into..."
