  s06: <
    handle: "custom-boof/06"
    type: "custom-boof"
    excerpt: "Boof reached out, hoping to touch the shadow, to understand it. \"Is this what the Fool wanted me to see?\" Boof wondered. The shadow flickered and danced, evading their grasp."
